name: Funny Face Frittata Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Ask mum or dad to preheat the oven to 180Â°C. Line each muffin hole with a paper case.
To make the egg mixture, break eggs into a large jug and whisk together with milk.
To make the veggie mixture, mix the potato, carrot, peas and corn in a bowl. Divide veggie mixture between paper cases. Then pour egg mixture over the top and sprinkle with cheese.
Bake for 25 minutes until puffy and golden. Add veggies to make funny faces and cucumber or carrot strips for whiskers.
